  "description": {
    "zh": "所以你终于还是对塔科夫的生意更感兴趣是嘛，嗯哼？好吧，遇到我算你走运，我就是专门做这种差事的，来吧，刚好我手头就有一个差事……\n\n你先给我带一把卡什尼科夫步枪来给我怎么样？具体型号是什么不重要，主要耐久磨损还在接受范围内即可。很好，期待你的早日答复。",
    "en": "So you're interested in the business here in Tarkov, right? Good thing you met me then, I'm the right person for this, so let's get started, I got a job for you.\n\nBring me a few Kalashnikov rifles, make sure they're not broken. Not important what exact variant, as long as they are in an acceptable condition. Got it? Alright then, I expect to hear from you soon."
  },
